es and sells elevators, motors, and submersible pumps. It serves hydrocarbon, steel, nuclear, marine, and power industries; port, jetty, and refineries; and oil and gas industries. The company was formerly known as Lloyds Steels Industries Limited and changed its name to Lloyds Engineering Works Limited in July 2023. Lloyds Engineering Works Limited was founded in 1974 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}